"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-27-Historic-gender-parity-milestone-celebrated-at-Paris-Olympics-1vAhbjQStKU-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Copied  With the 2024 Olympic Games underway in Paris, we are witnessing a historic milestone in the fight for gender equality. For the first time ever, the Games will achieve gender parity, with equal numbers of male and female athletes competing. The landmark achievement is being celebrated through archives restored by Chinese tech giant Alibaba, featuring women in the Olympics who have made history. CGTN's Feng Yilei has the details.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"